organizations.name: entire new episode of action bronson

text:
When it comes to food, no rapper is as invested in culinary skills quite like Action Bronson. To kick off the year, the rapper’s show Fuck, That’s Delicious returned to VICELAND for a brand new season.
In the first episode, Bronson takes viewers on a tour through the five boroughs of NYC, his hometown, to taste some of the finest local delicacies the city has to offer. The fact that the rapper is high throughout most of it, adds to the comedy value of the show. Unfortunately, there’s no word as to whether Action Bronson will be releasing any new music since his debut album Mr. Wonderful but tune into the show for a look into the rapper’s life.
Watch the latest episode of Action Bronson’s Fuck, That’s Delicious above now.
